---
title: Creamy Chicken Kumara Top Pie & Veggies with Parmesan Topping
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that warm and cosy craving with this rich, cheesy kumara mash-topped number. Chicken and veggies are cooked in a creamy sauce for an explosion of flavour and a dinner that reminds us why at-home cooking is best.
